{"tid":2435120,"cid":5,"subCid":11,"title":"司法人員遭電話騷擾及恐嚇　兩名男子被捕　警將交代案情","createTime":"2021-03-06T04:18:11.000Z","updateTime":"2021-03-06T09:54:40.000Z","uid":44209,"like":3,"dislike":25,"uniUserReply":16,"replies":[{"pid":"b558e2b0f8332b55613d78a490d073b262926581","tid":2435120,"uid":44209,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-03-06T04:18:11.000Z","msg":"司法人員遭恐嚇，兩名男子被捕。據了解，有人用電話騷擾司法人員，又在社交媒體出言恐嚇，兩名男子涉嫌干犯「電話、訊息或電報相關的罪行」及「煽惑他人傷人或對他人身體加以嚴重傷害」。警方將於今日（6日）下午1時交代案情，屆時《香港01》會進行直播。"},{"pid":"fcd2de7adc2c61078cde740be465cd55026d749e","tid":2435120,"uid":156652,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-03-06T04:19:46.000Z","msg":"無用太空？"},{"pid":"f0357f9c57b3a8ae75c47c88d6da1690e0fba465","tid":2435120,"uid":44209,"like":4,"dislike":1,"score":3,"quote":{"pid":"fcd2de7adc2c61078cde740be465cd55026d749e","tid":2435120,"uid":156652,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-03-06T04:19:46.000Z","msg":"無用太空？"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-03-06T04:22:05.000Z","msg":"自己部機，你換卡都冇用，有IMEI<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/math.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"fd399fae9dba3d32b6f74dcacda4d493b19bcdb6","tid":2435120,"uid":156652,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"f0357f9c57b3a8ae75c47c88d6da1690e0fba465","tid":2435120,"uid":44209,"like":4,"dislike":1,"score":3,"quote":{"pid":"fcd2de7adc2c61078cde740be465cd55026d749e","tid":2435120,"uid":156652,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-03-06T04:19:46.000Z","msg":"無用太空？"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-03-06T04:22:05.000Z","msg":"自己部機，你換卡都冇用，有IMEI<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/math.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-03-06T04:23:03.000Z","msg":"出去鴨記買部垃圾電話"},{"pid":"aaf02e457d45a4cd78956876d4dc1ae21aacfb3c","tid":2435120,"uid":156579,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-03-06T04:25:08.000Z","msg":"之前何官俾人寫大字拉到未<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"61b3e783828218fc4bafdcbcac480